64.5771-25/38974792_459450586856762_3358244016603382828_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KC8oV9ps4_QQ7kNvgGr39ZH&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlgEPibpu0l7VW8MaE95aWpTE7-ld5r2QaCllP3MRy4w&oe=67614EB9"}, {"file_name": "Recording_urinary_output_SS_05.png", "id": "480460224578456", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982699_480460227911789_6803552178662113930_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0vaO2vkTDDIQ7kNvgHxwOqF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAtH5coQPvbageC--Q5yfjaR8BulFdh7hdWD9d-UDAhpA&oe=67617697"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2560X1440.png", "id": "458101067138615", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974686_458101070471948_3126529237587478707_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RRSkC_Ds45oQ7kNvgHhmLQf&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDd7Lt0z-8Uen1o81E4o5h5AfjSgWsiO79cepTe7_MR-g&oe=67614B0B"}, "display_name": "Recording Urinary Output Simulator", "keywords": [], "long_description": "In this tutorial, learners will engage in a VR simulation to measure and record urinary output. The process includes preparation, patient communication, measurement, and documentation. By the end of this tutorial, participants will be able to: \n- Remember the steps for measuring and recording urinary output. \n- Understand the importance of accurate measurements in patient care. \n- Apply the procedures in a clinical setting to ensure patient safety and data accuracy. \n- Analyze and identify potential issues or abnormalities in urinary output. \n- Evaluate their techniques and make necessary adjustments for improvement. \n- Create accurate and comprehensive records of urinary output for further clinical evaluation. \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to assist patients with feeding efficiently and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_d